<h1>Resources</h1>
<p>Below are additional ways you can learn more about depression and contact information for doctors and help centers. 
<div class="resource-options col-xs-12">
	<h2>Suicide Hotline</h2>
	<p><a href="1-800-273-8255">1-800-273-8255</a>. Save this number to your phone contacts in one click to have it accessible for an emergency.</p>
	<button class="col-xs-12 btn btn-primary">Save to Phone</button>
	<h2>Educate yourself</h2>
	<p>Check out <a href="#" >Web MD</a> or <a href="#" >Mayo Clinic</a> for deeper analysis of depression symptoms and causes.</p>
	<button class="col-xs-12 btn btn-primary">Learn More</button>
	<h2>Doctors in Your Area</h2>
	<p>Find a phychologist or psychiatrist in your area.</p>
	<button class="col-xs-12 btn btn-primary">Find a Doctor Recommendation</button>
</div>
<div class="next-step-container">
	<%= link_to "Next Step", learn_path, class: "next-step" %>
	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
</div>